               <p>This accession consists of general correspondence to John Blum arranged alphabetically by correspondent. Congratulatory messages on the publication of Blum's memoir, <emph render="italic">A Life in History</emph> (2004), and his New Haven- based murder mystery, <emph render="italic">An Old Blue Corpse</emph> (2005) are included.</p>
